        <p>The Seller agrees to pay a one-time platform fee of <strong>$1,500</strong>. This fee covers the listing of the property on the platform, professional listing services, offer management system, and digital closing tracking. The Seller fee is only due at the time of closing.</p>

        <h6>Additional Terms:</h6>
        <ul>
            <li>There are no hidden fees charged by the platform outside of the disclosed Buyer and Seller fees.</li>
            <li>Standard closing costs, such as title fees, taxes, and other customary costs, still apply and are the responsibility of the respective parties.</li>
